              "fldf7VQb6n7lxLM7F"
            ],
            "prompt": [
              "You are an expert AI summarizer assigned to generate a structured JSON summary of a media outlet’s attributes and insights.\n\nYour task:\n\nBased on available information about a media outlet, create a JSON object containing only the fields that have valid data. Each field must be represented as a key-value pair, using plain text values. Do not include any fields with missing, null, or empty values.\n\n### Required Fields (include only if data is available):\n- media_outlet_name\n- media_type\n- media_subcategory\n- subject_matter\n- communities_served\n- languages\n- publishing_frequency\n- geographic_focus\n- ai_generated_description\n- ai_publication_details_summary\n- ai_media_type_print_rates_summary\n- ai_media_type_digital_rates_summary\n- ai_media_type_radio_rates_summary\n- ai_media_type_tv_rates_summary\n\n### Output Format:\nRespond with a valid JSON object using the following pattern:\n{\n \"media_outlet_name\": \"Example Media\",\n \"media_type\": \"Print\",\n \"subject_matter\": \"Cultural and community news\",\n \"languages\": \"English, Spanish\",\n \"ai_generated_description\": \"A trusted media outlet serving diverse neighborhoods.\"\n}\n\nContext and Data:\nName: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldAB5HRkCQ0bKCpB"
                }
              },
              "\nType: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldvXgWdlUVzEYCqf"
                }
              },
